span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">498</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">249</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">&nbsp;kJ/mol</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>Summe: <span><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>685</mn><mtext>&nbsp;kJ/mol</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">685 \\text{ kJ/mol}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">685</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">&nbsp;kJ/mol</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Produkte:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mtext>O-H</mtext><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>463</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>926</mn><mtext>&nbsp;kJ/mol</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2 \\times \\text{O-H}: 2 \\times 463 = 926 \\text{ kJ/mol}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7278em; vertical-align: -0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">O-H</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">:</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7278em; vertical-align: -0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">463</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">926</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">&nbsp;kJ/mol</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>685</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>926</mn><mo>=</mo><mrow><mtext mathvariant=\"bold\">-241</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext mathvariant=\"bold\">kJ/mol</mtext></mrow><mspace width=\"1em\"></mspace><mtext>(exotherm)</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Delta H = 685 - 926 = \\textbf{-241 kJ/mol} \\quad \\text{(exotherm)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.0813em;\">H</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7278em; vertical-align: -0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">685</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">926</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textbf\">-241&nbsp;kJ/mol</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 1em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">(exotherm)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<h2 id=\"aktivierungsenergie\">Aktivierungsenergie</h2>\n<p>Die <strong>Aktivierungsenergie</strong> Eₐ ist die minimale Energie, die Reaktanten benötigen, um eine Reaktion zu starten.</p>\n<pre tabindex=\"0\"><code>         Aktivierungsenergie (Eₐ)\n                  ↓\nEdukte ─────────→ Übergangszustand ─────────→ Produkte\n           ↑                    ↑\n           |                    |\n      Reaktionsweg          Energie\n</code></pre><h3 id=\"katalysatoren\">Katalysatoren</h3>\n<p>Ein <strong>Katalysator</strong> senkt die Aktivierungsenergie, ohne selbst verbraucht zu werden.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beispiele</strong>: Enzyme in der Biologie, Platin im Katalysatorauto</li>\n<li><strong>Vorteil</strong>: Reaktion läuft bei niedrigerer Temperatur ab</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"spontaneität-von-reaktionen\">Spontaneität von Reaktionen</h2>\n<p>Nicht jede exotherme Reaktion läuft spontan ab. Die Spontaneität hängt von zwei Faktoren ab:</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-enthalpie-δh\">1. Enthalpie (ΔH)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>ΔH &lt; 0: Begünstigt spontane Reaktion</li>\n<li>ΔH &gt; 0: Ungünstig für spontane Reaktion</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-entropie-δs\">2. Entropie (ΔS)</h3>\n<p>Die <strong>Entropie</strong> ist ein Maß für die Unordnung eines Systems.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ΔS &gt; 0: Zunahme der Unordnung (begünstigend)</li>\n<li>ΔS &lt; 0: Abnahme der Unordnung (ungünstig)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"gibbs-energie-δg\">Gibbs-Energie (ΔG)</h3>\n<p>Die <strong>freie Enthalpie</strong> (Gibbs-Energie) entscheidet über Spontaneität:</p>\n<pre tabindex=\"0\"><code>ΔG = ΔH - T·ΔS\n</code></pre><ul>\n<li><strong>ΔG &lt; 0</strong>: Reaktion läuft spontan ab</li>\n<li><strong>ΔG &gt; 0</strong>: Reaktion läuft nicht spontan ab</li>\n<li><strong>ΔG = 0</strong>: System im Gleichgewicht</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"beispiel-bei-verschiedenen-temperaturen\">Beispiel bei verschiedenen Temperaturen</h3>\n<p>Für die Reaktion: N₂O₄(s) → 2NO₂(g)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ΔH = +57 kJ/mol (endotherm)</li>\n<li>ΔS = +176 J/(mol·K) (Zunahme der Unordnung)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Bei T = 298 K (25°C):\nΔG = 57 - 298·0,176 = +4,6 kJ/mol (nicht spontan)</p>\n<p>Bei T = 400 K (127°C):\nΔG = 57 - 400·0,176 = -13,4 kJ/mol (spontan)</p>\n<h2 id=\"energetische-diagramme\">Energetische Diagramme</h2>\n<h3 id=\"exotherme-reaktion\">Exotherme Reaktion</h3>\n<pre tabindex=\"0\"><code>Energie\n  ↑\n  │    Edukte\n  │─────╲\n  │      ╲\n  │       ╲ ΔH &lt; 0\n  │        ╲\n  │         ╲_________ Produkte\n  │\n  └──────────────────→ Reaktionskoordinate\n</code></pre><h3 id=\"endotherme-reaktion\">Endotherme Reaktion</h3>\n<pre tabindex=\"0\"><code>Energie\n  ↑\n  │              Produkte\n  │              ╱\n  │             ╱ ΔH &gt; 0\n  │            ╱\n  │    Edukte ╱\n  │─────╱─────\n  │\n  └──────────────────→ Reaktionskoordinate\n</code></pre><h2 id=\"praktische-anwendungen\">Praktische Anwendungen</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-heizwerte-und-brennwerte\">1. Heizwerte und Brennwerte</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Heizwert</strong>: Energie bei Verbrennung ohne Wasserkondensation</li>\n<li><strong>Brennwert</strong>: Energie inklusive Kondensationswärme von Wasser</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Beispiel Methan:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Heizwert: 36 MJ/kg</li>\n<li>Brennwert: 39,8 MJ/kg</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-neutralisationswärme\">2. Neutralisationswärme</h3>\n<p>Die Neutralisation von starken Säuren und Laugen:</p>\n<pre tabindex=\"0\"><code>H⁺ + OH⁻ → H₂O     ΔH = -57,6 kJ/mol\n</code></pre><h3 id=\"3-lösungsenergie\">3. Lösungsenergie</h3>\n<p>Beim Lösen von Stoffen:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Gitterenergie</strong> wird benötigt (endotherm)</li>\n<li><strong>Hydratationsenergie</strong> wird freigesetzt (exotherm)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Gesamt: ΔH = Hydratationsenergie - Gitterenergie</p>\n<h2 id=\"experimente\">Experimente</h2>\n<h3 id=\"experiment-1-exotherme-reaktion\">Experiment 1: Exotherme Reaktion</h3>\n<p><strong>Materialien</strong>: Stahlwolle, Feuerzeug, Wärmefläschchen</p>\n<p><strong>Durchführung</strong>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Stahlwolle entzünden</li>\n<li>In ein Wärmefläschchen halten</li>\n<li>Temperaturanstieg messen</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Erklärung</strong>: Oxidation von Eisen ist exotherm (ΔH &lt; 0)</p>\n<h3 id=\"experiment-2-endotherme-reaktion\">Experiment 2: Endotherme Reaktion</h3>\n<p><strong>Materialien</strong>: Bariumhydroxid, Ammoniumthiocyanat, Holzblock, Tropfen Wasser</p>\n<p><strong>Durchführung</strong>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Beide Stoffe mischen</li>\n<li>Mischung auf Holzblock mit Wasserstropfen stellen</li>\n<li>Wasser gefriert fest</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Erklärung</strong>: Lösungsvorgang ist endotherm (ΔH &gt; 0)</p>\n<h2 id=\"lernziele\">Lernziele</h2>\n<p>Nach Abschluss dieses Themenbereichs sollten Sie:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>✅ Exotherme und endotherme Reaktionen unterscheiden können</li>\n<li>✅ Die Reaktionsenthalpie ΔH berechnen können</li>\n<li>✅ Den Hessschen Satz anwenden können</li>\n<li>✅ Bindungsenthalpien nutzen können</li>\n<li>✅ Aktivierungsenergie und Katalyse erklären können</li>\n<li>✅ Die Spontaneität mit ΔG beurteilen können</li>\n<li>✅ Energetische Diagramme interpretieren können</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"weiterführende-themen\">Weiterführende Themen</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/themenbereiche/gleichgewicht-geschwindigkeit/\">Gleichgewicht und Geschwindigkeit</a> – Reaktionskinetik</li>\n<li><a href=\"/themenbereiche/redox-elektrochemie/\">Redoxreaktionen und Elektrochemie</a> – Elektrochemische Energie</li>\n<li><a href=\"/themenbereiche/analytische-methoden/\">Analytische Methoden</a> – Kalorimetrie</li>\n</ul>\n\n        </article>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n        <aside class=\"thema-sidebar\">\n          \n          <div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n            <div class=\"panel-heading\">\n              <h4><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-left\"></i> Zurück</h4>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"panel-body\">\n              <a href=\"/themenbereiche/\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-block\">Alle Themenbereiche</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </aside>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.thema-container {\n  margin-top: 30px;\n  margin-bottom: 40px;\n}\n\n.thema-header {\n  margin-bottom: 30px;\n}\n\n.thema-icon {\n  font-size: 4rem;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n}\n\n.thema-metadata {\n  margin-top: 15px;\n}\n\n.thema-content {\n  font-size: 1.1rem;\n  line-height: 1.8;\n}\n\n.thema-content h2 {\n  margin-top: 40px;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n  padding-bottom: 10px;\n  border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;\n}\n\n.thema-content h3 {\n  margin-top: 30px;\n  margin-bottom: 15px;\n}\n\n.label-difficulty {\n  font-size: 0.9rem;\n  padding: 5px 10px;\n}\n\n.label-grundlagen {\n  background-color: #28a745;\n}\n\n.label-mittelstufe {\n  background-color: #ffc107;\n  color: #000;\n}\n\n.label-fortgeschritten {\n  background-color: #dc3545;\n}\n\n \n@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\n  .thema-content {\n    color: #e0e0e0;\n  }\n\n  .thema-content h2 {\n    border-bottom-color: #0056b3;\n  }\n\n  .panel {\n    background-color: #3c3c3c;\n    border-color: #555;\n    color: #e0e0e0;\n  }\n\n  .panel-body {\n    color: #e0e0e0;\n    border-color: #555;\n  }\n}\n</style>\n\n\n<style>\n \n.themenbereiche-container {\n  margin-top: 20px;\n  margin-bottom: 40px;\n}\n\n \n.filter-controls {\n  background-color: #f8f9fa;\n  padding: 20px;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n}\n\n.filter-group {\n  margin-bottom: 15px;\n}\n\n.filter-group:last-child {\n  margin-bottom: 0;\n}\n\n.filter-group label {\n  font-weight: 600;\n  margin-right: 10px;\n  color: #495057;\n}\n\n.btn-group .btn {\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  margin-right: 5px;\n  transition: all 0.2s;\n}\n\n.btn-filter.active,\n.btn-filter:hover,\n.btn-type-filter.active,\n.btn-type-filter:hover {\n  transform: scale(1.05);\n}\n\n.search-group input {\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  padding-left: 15px;\n  border: 1px solid #ced4da;\n}\n\n.search-group input:focus {\n  border-color: #007bff;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.25);\n}\n\n \n.difficulty-grundlagen {\n  border-left: 5px solid #28a745 !important;\n}\n\n.difficulty-mittelstufe {\n  border-left: 5px solid #ffc107 !important;\n}\n\n.difficulty-fortgeschritten {\n  border-left: 5px solid #dc3545 !important;\n}\n\n.difficulty-alle {\n  border-left: 5px solid #6c757d !important;\n}\n\n \n.card {\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.topic-card {\n  opacity: 1;\n  transform: scale(1);\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.topic-card.hidden {\n  display: none;\n}\n\n.card .panel {\n  height: 100%;\n  transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n}\n\n.card .panel:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-5px);\n  box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n}\n\n.index-anchor {\n  text-decoration: none;\n  color: inherit;\n  display: block;\n}\n\n.panel-body h3.panel-title {\n  font-size: 1.1rem;\n  margin: 0;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\n.interactive-badge {\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n  animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n}\n\n@keyframes pulse {\n  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n  50% { opacity: 0.6; }\n}\n\n.panel-footer {\n  background-color: #f8f9fa;\n  border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;\n  border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;\n}\n\n.label-primary {\n  background-color: #007bff;\n}\n\n \n@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\n  .filter-controls {\n    background-color: #2c2c2c;\n  }\n\n  .filter-group label {\n    color: #e0e0e0;\n  }\n\n  .panel {\n    background-color: #3c3c3c;\n    border-color: #555;\n    color: #e0e0e0;\n  }\n\n  .panel-body {\n    color: #e0e0e0;\n    border-color: #555;\n  }\n\n  .search-group input {\n    background-color: #3c3c3c;\n    border-color: #555;\n    color: #e0e0e0;\n  }\n\n  .search-group input::placeholder {\n    color: #999;\n  }\n\n  .search-group input:focus {\n    background-color: #4c4c4c;\n    border-color: #007bff;\n    color: #fff;\n  }\n\n  .panel-footer {\n    background-color: #333;\n    border-top-color: #555;\n  }\n\n  .card .panel:hover {\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n  }\n}\n\n \n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .filter-controls {\n    padding: 15px;\n  }\n\n  .btn-group {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 5px;\n  }\n\n  .btn-group .btn {\n    flex: 1;\n    min-width: 80px;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    padding: 8px 12px;\n  }\n\n  .search-group input {\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n\n   \n  .thema-content-layout .row {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n\n  .thema-content-layout .col-md-8,\n  .thema-content-layout .col-md-4 {\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .thema-sidebar {\n    margin-top: 20px;\n  }\n\n  .thema-content p {\n    display: block;\n    visibility: visible;\n  }\n}\n</style>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n  const topicCards = document.querySelectorAll('.topic-card');\n  const noResults = document.getElementById('no-results');\n\n  \n  const filterButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.btn-filter');\n  const typeFilterButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.btn-type-filter');\n  const searchInput = document.getElementById('search-input');\n\n  let currentDifficultyFilter = 'all';\n  let currentTypeFilter = 'all';\n  let currentSearchTerm = '';\n\n  \n  filterButtons.forEach(button => {\n    button.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      filterButtons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));\n      this.classList.add('active');\n      currentDifficultyFilter = this.dataset.filter;\n      applyFilters();\n    });\n  });\n\n  \n  typeFilterButtons.forEach(button => {\n    button.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      typeFilterButtons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));\n      this.classList.add('active');\n      currentTypeFilter = this.dataset.type;\n      applyFilters();\n    });\n  });\n\n  \n  searchInput.addEventListener('input', function() {\n    currentSearchTerm = this.value.toLowerCase();\n    applyFilters();\n  });\n\n  function applyFilters() {\n    let visibleCount = 0;\n\n    topicCards.forEach(card => {\n      const schwierigkeit = card.dataset.schwierigkeit;\n      const isInteraktiv = card.dataset.interaktiv === 'true';\n      const title = card.dataset.title;\n      const description = card.dataset.description;\n\n      \n      const matchesDifficulty = currentDifficultyFilter === 'all' ||\n                                 schwierigkeit === currentDifficultyFilter;\n      const matchesType = currentTypeFilter === 'all' ||\n                         (currentTypeFilter === 'interaktiv' && isInteraktiv);\n      const matchesSearch = currentSearchTerm === '' ||\n                           title.includes(currentSearchTerm) ||\n                           description.includes(currentSearchTerm);\n\n      if (matchesDifficulty && matchesType && matchesSearch) {\n        card.classList.remove('hidden');\n        visibleCount++;\n      } else {\n        card.classList.add('hidden');\n      }\n    });\n\n    \n    noResults.style.display = visibleCount === 0 ? 'block' : 'none';\n  }\n});\n</script>\n\n\n        </main>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer class=\"site-footer\" style=\"margin-top: 50px; padding: 30px 0; background-color: #333; color: #fff;\" role=\"contentinfo\" aria-label=\"Website-Fußzeile\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h4>chemie-lernen.org - 📖 Offene, 🖱️ Interaktive und 🥽 Immersive Lerninhalte</h4>\n                <p>chemie-lernen.org - Ihre Plattform für innovative Chemie-Lernräume in Virtual Reality. Machen Sie komplexe chemische Konzepte greifbar und erlebbar.</p>\n                <p>\n                    <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/c/chemie_lernen_org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;\" aria-label=\"Besuchen Sie unseren Patreon\">\n                        <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom; margin-right: 5px;\">\n                            <path d=\"M4.231 0C3.281 0 2.4.513 2.4 1.484v20.922c0 .995.881 1.484 1.831 1.484.95 0 1.774-.49 1.774-1.484V1.484C6.005.513 5.181 0 4.231 0zm13.396 4.453c-2.606 0-4.748 2.054-4.748 4.578 0 2.525 2.142 4.579 4.748 4.579s4.748-2.054 4.748-4.579c0-2.524-2.142-4.578-4.748-4.578z\"></path>\n                        </svg>\n                        Unterstütze uns auf Patreon\n                    </a>\n                </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 text-right\">\n                <p>© 2025 chemie-lernen.org - 📖 Offene, 🖱️ Interaktive und 🥽 Immersive Lerninhalte. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.</p>\n                <p><small><a href=\"/impressum/\" style=\"color: #fff;\">impressum</a> | <a href=\"/datenschutz/\" style=\"color: #fff;\">datenschutz</a></small></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</footer>\n    \n\n  <script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.2/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/js/bootstrap.min.js\"></script>\n\n  \n  <script src=\"/js/dark-mode.js\"></script>\n\n  \n  <script src=\"/js/quiz-system.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/js/quiz-user-system.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/js/progress-tracker.js\"></script>\n\n  \n  \n  <script src=\"/data/quiz-energetik.js\"></script>\n  \n\n  \n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/contrib/mhchem.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <script>\n    document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n      renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n        delimiters: [\n          {left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},\n          {left: '$', right: '$', display: false},\n          {left: '\\\\[', right: '\\\\]', display: true},\n          {left: '\\\\(', right: '\\\\)', display: false}\n        ]\n      });\n    });\n  </script>\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n\n</body></html>"},"afterSnapshot":"after@call@173"}
{"type":"frame-snapshot","snapshot":{"callId":"call@173","snapshotName":"after@call@173","pageId":"page@26e4637a7e554862b12d46a99a15a259","frameId":"frame@9f03b90b234b369bf1b58f130a478b49","frameUrl":"https://chemie-lernen.org/themenbereiche/energetik/","doctype":"html","html":[[6,4130]],"viewport":{"width":1280,"height":720},"timestamp":21116.664,"wallTime":1767213745460,"collectionTime":12.700000047683716,"resourceOverrides":[],"isMainFrame":true}}
